  "text": "Adaptive Intelligent Web Based Educational Systems (AIWBES) or adaptive hypermedia provide an alternative to the traditional, just-put-it-on-the-web approach in the development of web based educational courseware. An AIWBES provides adaptivity in terms of goals, preferences, and knowledge of individual students during interaction with the system [CITATION_1] .",
